const renderCarDetails = () => { if (!selectedCar) return null; return (

{selectedCar.make} {selectedCar.model} ({selectedCar.year})

Description: {selectedCar.description}
Odometer: {selectedCar.odometer} km
Vehicle Condition: {selectedCar.car_condition}

Sale Details

Sale Location: {selectedCar.state}
Sale Category: {selectedCar.sales_category}
Sale Date: {selectedCar.sale_date}
Sale Price: ${selectedCar.sale_price}
Salvage Vehicle: {selectedCar.salvage_vehicle ? "Yes" : "No"}
); };
